Collection Description
THEBULLBREWCOLLECTION is a limited membership NFT collection of 1,000 passes deployed on Arbitrum Nova.
Each BRW NFT serves as a digital membership credential granting access to future benefits, exclusive experiences, community privileges, token-gated content, promotions, and ecosystem participation.
Ownership of a BRW NFT is verifiable on-chain and can be used by websites, applications, Discord integrations, and future partner platforms to authenticate membership status.
The collection is permanently capped at 1,000 memberships.
